{
  "name": "Green Roads — Daily Publisher Scraper",
  "nodes": [
    {
      "parameters": {
        "content": "## Green Roads — Daily Publisher Contact Scraper\n\n**Schedule:** Daily 09:00 AM UTC\n**Sources:** AWIN API + AWIN UI Profile Scrape + Hunter.io\n**Output:** Tab 1 (Publishers), Tab 2 (Skipped), Tab 3 (Rate Limit Log)\n**API limits:** AWIN 20 req/min · Hunter ~10 req/min\n\n⚠️ Refresh AWIN session cookie every 24-48 hours.\n\n### Workflow variables required (set under Workflow → Variables):\n- `AWIN_ADVERTISER_ID`\n- `SHEET_ID`\n- `HUNTER_MONTHLY_LIMIT` (default 480)\n- `LOW_CLICK_THRESHOLD` (default 100)\n- `ZERO_ACTIVITY_THRESHOLD` (default 2)\n- `TIMEZONE` (default UTC)\n\n### Credentials to map after import:\n- `AWIN_API_TOKEN` (httpHeaderAuth → Authorization: Bearer …)\n- `AWIN_SESSION_COOKIE` (httpHeaderAuth → Cookie: …)\n- `HUNTER_API_KEY` (httpQueryAuth → api_key=…)\n- `GOOGLE_SHEETS_OAUTH` (Google Sheets OAuth2)",
        "height": 460,
        "width": 540,
        "color": 4
      },
      "id": "sticky_header",
      "name": "Sticky — Workflow Header",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote",
      "typeVersion": 1,
      "position": [-400, -480]
    },
